\N<Syouta>Good, good, this spot isn't blocked either.

\N<Syouta>That's right! This leads to the area where the "mid-boss" of
the 11th floor is, so this is the last shortcut.
\N<Syouta>...So, come on, get injust like before.
\N<Luna>Ugh... I want Syouta-kun to go in first this time...

\N<Syouta>Huh? What if your big butt and boobs get stuck? Who's gonna
push from behind? If I'm in front, I can't help you out.

\N<Syouta>Just hurry up and go before we get spotted by a monster!
Quick, quick!!

Will you proceed through the shortcut to the "11th floor"
that Syouta has suggested again?

Luna was reluctant because she thought Syouta might play a
trick on her again, but she prioritized the benefit of
reaching the mid-boss area and proceeded through the narrow
hole.
A reminiscence scene has been added.
"1_t=5_subject=It's tough, but this is exactly the time we have to overcome together"
"1_t=6_subject=We may have our disagreements, but we trust each other, so it's all good"

\N<Syouta>Heheh, I feel like I'm getting a surge of power. Right now,
I could beat any monster! Even the mid-boss isn't scary!

\N<Luna>Haah... haah... You're so energetic... I don't even feel
like getting angry anymore.

\N<Syouta>Are you tired from coming? Well, after such a flashy climax,
that's to be expected.
Notification: There is a new post on SNS.

\N<Luna>Hmm, I won't go in because it seems like Syouta-kun will
play another trick on me Let's just proceed normally
through the dungeon--

\N<Syouta>Eeeh!? There's a shortcut and you're choosing to take the
long way around!? Besides, it's not my fault you tried to
turn back halfway through.

\N<Luna>I've already decided, so I'm not going in This area is
really cold, so let's hurry to the deepest part

Ignoring Syouta's bored expression, Luna left the spot and
began to move further into the dungeon.
